    libnotify-dev-gtk2.10 for the Gtk 2.10 specific API; let libnotify1
    provide libnotify1-gtk2.10 for the Gtk 2.10 specific ABI; set libnotify1's
    shlibs to "libnotify1 (>= 0.4.3), libnotify1-gtk2.10".

